Manny Pérez https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Manny_P%C3%A9rez 0 Manuel "Manny" Pérez Batista (born May 5, 1969) is a Dominican American actor who has appeared in the television series Third Watch and in the film Washington Heights. He is the cousin of Pulitzer Prize-winning author Junot Diaz.
